## Derivation

The Van't Hoff equation can be derived from the ***Gibbs-Helmholtz equation***, which states that:

$$\left( \frac{\partial (G/T) } {\partial T} \right)_p = - \frac {H} {T^2}$$

Regular form:

$$\frac{d}{dT} K_p = \frac{\delta H}{RT^2}


